{"tid":393471,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"11月尾 獨遊大阪京都","createTime":"2017-09-09T09:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T08:04:18.000Z","uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9df2cf39236bf108853ffe498bcbf993b50dde","tid":393471,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:45:09.000Z","msg":"今年11月尾會去大阪京都<br />\n<br />\nDay1 : 2點15分到關西機場, 黑門市場, HARUKAS 300 <br />\n<br />\nDay2 : USJ ,心齋橋<br />\n<br />\nDay3 : 會神咁早去京都 嵐山, 金閣寺<br />\n<br />\nDay4 : 山崎蒸餾所 下午未plan<br />\n<br />\nDay5 : 會去廣島 原爆, 兔島<br />\n<br />\nDay6 : 宮島(紅葉谷公園,落鳥居)<br />\n<br />\nDay7 : hea, 15:15機走<br />\n<br />\n會周圍影相, 想放鬆下,行程應該唔會太趕<br />\n我遇到個問題就係嵐山小火車訂票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkday.com/zh-hk/product/10471?cid=2636&amp;ud1=Cantonese&amp;ud2=jp_10471&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwos7NBRAWEiwAypNCe_kqQtoujxkBj_pIWWTfpXKY0wnWoRdZX-acL1mCfEcXPYiW4cxn8xoCb4QQAvD_BwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkday.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fproduct%2F10471%3Fcid%3D2636%26ud1%3DCantonese%26ud2%3Djp_10471%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjwos7NBRAWEiwAypNCe_kqQtoujxkBj_pIWWTfpXKY0wnWoRdZX-acL1mCfEcXPYiW4cxn8xoCb4QQAvD_BwE&d=B0JB2woox3lLUaq5Avl%2BIXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ea7e1144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkday.com/zh-hk/product/10471?cid=2636&amp;ud1=Cantonese&amp;ud2=jp_10471&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwos7NBRAWEiwAypNCe_kqQtoujxkBj_pIWWTfpXKY0wnWoRdZX-acL1mCfEcXPYiW4cxn8xoCb4QQAvD_BwE</a><br />\n我係呢個網到睇,有得訂,但冇得揀單雙數<br />\n又冇朋友係日本可以幫我買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咩建議???<br />\n同埋我呢個行程買關西5 day pass抵唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"4d33285175af7bad96f6cbb002af57b873584d13","tid":393471,"uid":128550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"關西有5 day pass ?"},{"pid":"2f32c8720781020e588bc3c3c37ab0aa4ccacaf2","tid":393471,"uid":137924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:51:0