quote><br />\n我影相應該都有排影，同埋想個節奏慢啲，去下tea咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff6a9d30b724c7dd51d41c1426f20b449418934","tid":393471,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>關西有5 day pass ?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_wide/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_wide%2F&d=B0JB2woox3lLUaq5Avl%2BIXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=108e807d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_wide/</a><br />\n有的</blockquote><br />\n 原來係依張 我覺得好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係貴啊,但我想去廣島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔知抵唔抵,睇下有冇手足知道<br />\n比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_hiroshima%2F&d=B0JB2woox3lLUaq5Avl%2BIXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=56b20f44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/</a><br />\n<br />\n廣島係要呢張</blockquote><br />\n巴打你啱，頭兩日可能買多個單單大阪嘅2 day pass"},{"pid":"1842e3ceb3ecf4f80cdccd4a71c5f4af5c5e7e69","tid":393471,"uid":4370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"我都係月尾但未開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb556d284b3e496930a9af3dfb113492763279d","tid":393471,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係月尾但未開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要開始啦.始終旺季<br />\n啲好酒店好多已經冇哂"},{"pid":"d558493a7a7a9a47112308e64b271a6a1ea407a7","tid":393471,"uid":16963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"不如落機直去京都去啲近嘅景點 喺京都瞓一晚 第二朝去嵐山 好過你晨早喺大阪上京都"},{"pid":"295864f1832f402795cb0463d84c725ba36bfaf9","tid":393471,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如落機直去京都去啲近嘅景點 喺京都瞓一晚 第二朝去嵐山 好過你晨早喺大阪上京都</blockquote><br />\n我啱啱都諗過黎<br />\n打算改成D1-D2 大阪<br />\nD3-D4京都<br />\nD5-D7 廣島<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d67a05fe4548cc1ecd34bddad889e387406ad43","tid":393471,"uid":4370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係月尾但未開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要開始啦.始終旺季<br />\n啲好酒店好多已經冇哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大阪是咪住難波好？<br />\n<br />\n但朋友推介一間唔錯嘅但離心齋橋嗰啲20-30分鐘車程"},{"pid":"e1ede17074bc6b0f6ba940eb1aecb6a1803894a2","tid":393471,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係月尾但未開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要開始啦.始終旺季<br />\n啲好酒店好多已經冇哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大阪是咪住難波好？<br />\n<br />\n但朋友推介一間唔錯嘅但離心齋橋嗰啲20-30分鐘車程</blockquote><br />\n我住hostel咋,心齋橋附近"},{"pid":"9fff30d80173567c601dc88ec6e371b5206d30f9","tid":393471,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"睇黎遲下要改改行程再開新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}